Private Sub AbaAlmHistorico_Click()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim INSTRUMENTO As String Dim TIPO As String
INSTRUMENTO = Replace(Text1.Caption, "-", "_") PONTEIRO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 4, 1)
If PONTEIRO = "_" Then ' Para todos os intrumentos (exceto PDICs e TDICs)
ALM_1 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) & "AHH" ALM_2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) & "AH" ALM_3 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) & "ALL" ALM_4 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) & "AL" FLT_1 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) & "AT" FLT_2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 3) NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 5) Else ' Para PDICs e TDICs ALM_1 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) & "AHH" ALM_2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) & "AH" ALM_3 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) & "ALL" ALM_4 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) & "AL" FLT_1 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) & "AT" FLT_2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 4) NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 6)
End If
' AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & NUMERO & "' And (EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_1 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_2 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_3 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_4 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & FLT_1 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & FLT_2 & "')" FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & NUMERO & "%' And (SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_1 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_2 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_3 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_4 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & FLT_1 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & FLT_2 & "%')"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim INSTRUMENTO As String Dim TIPO As String
INSTRUMENTO = Replace(Text1.Caption, "-", "_") PONTEIRO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 4, 1)
If PONTEIRO = "_" Then ' Para todos os intrumentos (exceto PDICs e TDICs)
ALM_1 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) & "AHH" ALM_2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) & "AH" ALM_3 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) & "ALL" ALM_4 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) & "AL" FLT_1 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) & "AT" FLT_2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 3) NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 5) Else ' Para PDICs e TDICs ALM_1 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) & "AHH" ALM_2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) & "AH" ALM_3 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) & "ALL" ALM_4 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) & "AL" FLT_1 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) & "AT" FLT_2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 4) NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 6)
End If
AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & NUMERO & "' And (EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_1 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_2 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_3 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & ALM_4 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & FLT_1 & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & FLT_2 & "')" ' FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & NUMERO & "%' And (SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_1 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_2 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_3 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & ALM_4 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & FLT_1 & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & FLT_2 & "%')"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
Private Sub NumericInput_CV_KeyDown(ByVal KeyCode As Integer, ByVal Shift As Integer)
If KeyCode = vbKeyReturn Then SendKeys "{F2}" End If
End Sub
Private Sub NumericInput_SP_KeyDown(ByVal KeyCode As Integer, ByVal Shift As Integer)
If KeyCode = vbKeyReturn Then SendKeys "{F1}" End If
End Sub
